    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">328 Mickle Street<ptr target="nyp.00540_n2"/></name>
                    <name type="place">Camden N J</name>
                    <date when="1885-05-24" rend="right">May 24<ptr target="nyp.00540_n1"/></date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear J B&#8212;</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>I am ab't in my usual general health, but <hi rend= "italic">lameness bad</hi>&#8212;had a fall a month ago,
                &#38; turned my ankle in&#8212;don't think I will be able to come up to West
                Park&#8212;</p>
            <closer> 
                <signed>W W</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>  
